text: Shilongo Filippus Uukule (1919 at Onyaanya - 2010) was senior headman of the Uukwanambwa, a clan of the Ovambo people in Namibia. His residence is located in the Onyaanya Constituency of the Oshikoto Region. == References == Category:Namibian people Category:1919 births Category:2010 deaths
title: Shilongo Uukule
